{"tid":2122661,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"[警世post] 假貨之都”莆田”  好多ig 鞋鋪係度入貨","createTime":"2020-07-24T06:28:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T10:41:12.000Z","uid":11496,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2d97df0be92e9cf5116418d16aca72cb8a6d5bff","tid":2122661,"uid":11496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:28:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/KxAW3t423rg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKxAW3t423rg&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6LM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=162fe3e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/KxAW3t423rg</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">香港好多賣假鞋ig shop 我諗就係係呢度入貨<br />\n出呢個post主要係想警世 <br />\n唔好同我講咩「原來仲有人咁on9 係ig shop買鞋  抵你死」 「唔上網買係基本」 呢d野 <br />\n呢個世界就係大把人咁on9   <br />\n尤其而家代購咁hit   好易貪方便信左<br />\n唔想再比班仆街係大陸入貨呃到好似我呢d 咁既on9水魚 <br />\n無門市  順豐交易更加要小心  好鬼<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>pick.a.size</strong></span> 賣假鞋</span><br />\n<br />\n由於全球化經濟的拓展，至今已有許多廠商為了減少生產成本，選擇在勞力低廉的地區設廠，其中又以中國福建省莆田市最為廣泛，也因此這座城市自然而然便成為假貨商最適合生存的地方。在此部紀錄片中，《Vice News》找到了一名從英國留學回來的假鞋賣家 Chan，並直擊他的工作室做深度訪談。透過網站的操作，Chan 的客戶來自全球各地，其中竟大部分都是像高中生、大學生這種年輕學生族群，Chan 表示：「他們都很聰明，他們知道雖然這些是假鞋但具有高品質，因此總是會來找我買這些高仿的複製品。」<br />\n此外 Chan 還說道：「儘管我們假貨供應商目前仍時常遭警察搜索，甚至還得面臨一些潛在的訴訟，但我就是有辦法繼續經營下去。」據了解，Chan 在英國留學時期就已經開始著手經銷假鞋一事，當時他每天都能生產 120 雙假鞋，平均每月的收入更是高達 10 萬美元（約新台幣 300 萬元），不過這對他而言卻還是不夠，因此他決定搬來莆田，為了就是要能更接近這些商品。<br />\n在 Chan 的工作室公寓中，我們能透過鏡頭看見各式各樣的高仿假鞋，包含像是時下最夯的「The Ten」系列、YEEZY 系列，甚至是較高端的 BALENCIAGA Triple&ndash;S 鞋款都應有盡有，而不管是鞋身外型，還是附上的小標籤，相似度簡直幾乎是完美等級，讓我們再次感受到假貨商的強大所帶來的震撼。不曉得大家對於此事有什麼看法？歡迎在底下留言討論。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HwuGXJ2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHwuGXJ2.jpg&h=85d4c66e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Gezyhn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Gezyhn.jpg&h=5b028d3a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cavrpo3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcavrpo3.jpg&h=658f4da4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FdvnHaJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFdvnHaJ.jpg&h=95722deb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gsbFtQK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgsbFtQK.jpg&h=af780e2c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dm8gMCp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDm8gMCp.jpg&h=0fb59711&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fALfhLz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfALfhLz.png&h=7629afb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n文章來源：<a href=\"https://m.juksy.com/archives/81731?atl=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.juksy.com%2Farchives%2F81731%3Fatl%3D1&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6LM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=35fe3f59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.juksy.com/archives/81731?atl=1</a>"},{"pid":"379bb92cdcd4dbf4ee4b691c0d377ea0d4a14d2a","tid":2122661,"uid":219583,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:30:16.000Z","msg":"一諗起賣假鞋就諗撚起雞wing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"300fb28e2fcb24758de339b79e330278bbf3411c","tid":2122661,"uid":11496,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"379bb92cdcd4dbf4ee4b691c0d377ea0d4a14d2a","tid":2122661,"uid":219583,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:30:16.000Z","msg":"一諗起賣假鞋就諗撚起雞wing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:32:30.000Z","msg":"佢賣過假鞋？ 完全唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkg